INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS

1. Download and install Drush (http://drush.ws/)
2. Download ans install Drush make (http://drupal.org/project/drush_make)
3. Clone or Fork the SoftActiva Drupal base repository (git://github.com/softactiva/Drupal-base.git)
4. Uncomment needed modules
5. Run: drush make --translations=en,es [build-path]
